    "text": "You chant a marching song of Yled to empower the undead and terrify the living. Undead creatures within the area gain the quickened condition for 1 minute, which they can use only to Stride.  \n Living creatures in the area must attempt a Will save. This gains the emotion, *fear*, and mental traits for living creatures.",
